data.title: Sanaya Irani Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Sanaya Irani with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Briefly co-hosted Zara Nachke Dikha with her boyfriend Mohit Sehgal

In 2012 she won the Best On-Screen Jodi award along with her co-star Barun Sobti of Iss Pyaar Ko Kya Naam Doon at both the People's Choice Awards India and the Indian Telly Awards

Was voted one of Asia's top ten sexiest women on a list published in 2013

Won the Asian Viewer's Television Awards Female Soap Personality of the Year award for her performances in Rangrasiya

In her early career she struggled with dialogues, as she did not yet speak Hindi well
